reviews.text:
WOW. Right off the bat, there's a sweet, juicy brightness that just shocks you into awareness (apple/cranberry), that's immediately followed by a fried, sugary pumpkin dough. Very tasty stuff. In the moments between inhale and exhale, you start to get this sweet syrup coating your throat just in time before pumpkin spice and vanilla bathe your tongue on the exhale, leaving a texture almost like your tongue is covered in powdered sugar, and If you can keep from hitting it again immediately(and you'll want to), swear to god, it's almost like there's little bits of orange marmalade nestled against the roof of your mouth. Caught myself licking at it, going "what the?!?". This one works absolutely all your taste buds save for salty, so it's a very engaging vape, and an absolute must try. Can easily be an adv, and is just a monster in all the right ways with that morning cuppa.&#xD;
&#xD;
Brilliant!
